wiki_detail.notes:
* Due to several character stats needing to be recalculated each time a character spawns, casting ''Requiem'' immediately upon respawning will cause its cooldown to be unaffected by ability haste. Damage dealt is unaffected due to cast time. {{bug}}
* ''Requiem's'' channel is telegraphed to all enemy champions by a beam of light that descends on all targets, including if they are {{tip|untargetable}} or even {{tip|death|dead}}.
* ''Requiem'' will affect {{tip|clone|clones}}.
* The damage will apply [[spell effects]] to targets in an order based on proximity to '''Karthus'''. Single target spell effects (such as {{ii|Luden's Companion}}) are thus triggered on the ''closest'' enemy champion.
* ''Requiem'' will not affect {{ci|Neeko}} if she's {{ai|I|Neeko|disguised}} as a non-champion if '''Karthus''' is affected by {{ai|Death Defied|Karthus}}.{{bug}}
